					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">There's a sequence of reads that the PPU does when it renders:<br /><br />Read nametable byte<br />Read attribute byte<br />Read tile byte 1<br />Read tile byte 2<br /><br />If you have a mapper in there that watches for the first read, then you can force the attribute read to do something else.</div>

					
